            "title": "Citi's Fraser on US Economy, China Presence",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\"><div class=\"vsly-player\" data-template=\"PVoSFh2nIXOPH\" id=\"yf_OiBCzUSM\" style=\"background:#ddd;padding-top:calc(56.25% + 24px);font-size:0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;width:100%;\"></div></div>\n                        Citigroup (C) Chief Executive Officer, Jane Fraser, speaks to Bloomberg's Stephen Engle about Citi's growing presence in China, the current state of the US economy, and her views on how to deploy AI in the financial sector.<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51681907');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
